    public class SearchWindow
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements Standardization
    This class houses the search window. It is responsible for setting the layout of the search window and assigning action listeners.

    Michael Vassilev 30068475, Vic Phan 30061885, Sebastian Contreras 30062418
